00:23:34.210 --> 00:23:42.429
It's not a natural food for them. And so,
I actually, it's sometimes to me, when I see

00:23:42.429 --> 00:23:46.660
chimps in captivity, when I see chimps dressed
up, it's just heartbreaking to me because

00:23:46.660 --> 00:23:50.520
it's not where in my heart I know chimps belong.

00:23:50.520 --> 00:23:58.470
And so, that's why get that image because
have shown them eating bananas on television

00:23:58.470 --> 00:24:02.841
and in pictures. But it's a not natural food
