00:42:45.200 --> 00:42:50.509
the history of her realizing that she's gotten
so much from the chimps and it was time for

00:42:50.509 --> 00:42:55.780
her to do something for them. So, I'm gonna
play this video. Again, I shot this, I guess

00:42:55.780 --> 00:42:58.640
around 1999, but it's still very relevant.

00:42:58.640 --> 00:42:59.979
