00:48:38.549 --> 00:48:45.160
right around here. And she is a manager of
the Wanda Bobowski Fund, which is a scholarship

00:48:45.160 --> 00:48:50.240
for young girls. And she came and visited
Gombe years ago, fell in love with the place,

00:48:50.240 --> 00:48:55.910
saw that especially young women had a very
rough time in the world there.

00:48:55.910 --> 00:49:03.180
And so now, over 200 young women have been
