00:52:03.749 --> 00:52:04.749
&gt;&gt;Male #11: For their territory?

00:52:04.749 --> 00:52:05.749
&gt;&gt;Bill Wallauer: Yeah.

00:52:05.749 --> 00:52:06.749
&gt;&gt;Male #11: You said they beat each other?

00:52:06.749 --> 00:52:07.749
