00:52:12.119 --> 00:52:18.029
&gt;&gt;Bill Wallauer: The only genetic, as far
as spreading genetics from one community to

00:52:18.029 --> 00:52:24.349
another, the females do that. So, at about
age 12 or 13, when the females become reproductively

00:52:24.349 --> 00:52:28.430
active, they're likely to transfer from one
community to another. So, they are the only

00:52:28.430 --> 00:52:36.279
accepted ones. If a male gets caught on that
border trying, on that no chimp's land, he's

00:52:36.279 --> 00:52:37.989
definitely gonna get attacked.

00:52:37.989 --> 00:52:43.140
